37:52.604 --> 37:57.275
ARIA, STOP.
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BREAK UP
YOUR FAMILY TO KEEP US TOGETHER.

37:58.610 --> 37:59.811
THAT'S NOT A CHOICE.

38:05.651 --> 38:07.619
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

38:07.653 --> 38:12.358
I'LL... ( sighs )

38:12.391 --> 38:15.627
PROBABLY HEAD UP
TO MY FOLKS' PLACE FOR A WHILE,

38:15.661 --> 38:20.332
REGROUP, SEND OUT RESUMES,
MAKE COLD CALLS.

38:22.568 --> 38:24.503
WHEN WILL YOU BE BACK?

38:31.643 --> 38:35.347
ARIA...

38:35.381 --> 38:39.885
IF I CAN'T TEACH HIGH SCHOOL
IN THIS TOWN, OR COLLEGE,

38:39.918 --> 38:43.389
WHAT'S LEFT?

38:43.422 --> 38:47.092
IT'S WHAT I DO...

38:47.125 --> 38:50.529
AND I NEED TO FIND
A PLACE WHERE I CAN DO IT.

38:58.136 --> 38:59.438
( sniffles )

39:02.608 --> 39:06.077
