39:37.976 --> 39:39.010
* WITH YOU

39:55.494 --> 40:01.700
* NO, I...

40:19.751 --> 40:20.986
WHAT ALL SHOULD WE TAKE?

40:21.019 --> 40:22.588
WAIT, PUT THAT
IN THE DUFFEL BAG.

40:22.621 --> 40:24.856
WE HAVE
TO GIVE THEM EVERYTHING.

40:24.890 --> 40:26.091
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING FOR?

40:26.124 --> 40:28.494
I HAVE NO IDEA.

40:28.527 --> 40:31.162
THIS FEELS REALLY WEIRD,
GIVING THEM ALL OF ALI'S STUFF.

40:31.196 --> 40:33.899
WELL, MAYBE THERE'S SOMETHING
IN HERE THAT THE POLICE CAN USE.

40:33.932 --> 40:35.601
ALISON EVEN SAID THERE WAS.

40:35.634 --> 40:37.469
WHAT? WHEN?

40:37.503 --> 40:39.471
YESTERDAY.

40:39.505 --> 40:40.739
IN A DREAM.

40:40.772 --> 40:43.141
OKAY, WHY AM I JUST
HEARING ABOUT THIS NOW?

40:43.174 --> 40:44.976
( door closes )

40:51.850 --> 40:53.952
YOU WANT THIS IN THE BARN?
IT'S HEAVY.

40:53.985 --> 40:56.555
NO, IT'S NOT.
I'LL BE FINE.

40:56.588 --> 40:59.224
I DON'T WANT YOU
CARRYING ANY MORE
THAN YOU ALREADY ARE.

40:59.257 --> 41:00.959
( both chuckle )

41:06.097 --> 41:07.633
DO YOU WANT A BEER?

41:07.666 --> 41:09.167
YOU'RE OFF DUTY.

41:09.200 --> 41:12.638
UM, I'LL JUST TAKE
A SODA IF YOU GOT ONE.

41:12.671 --> 41:14.906
( floor creaking )

41:14.940 --> 41:16.675
IS SOMEONE ELSE HERE?

41:16.708 --> 41:18.644
I DON'T THINK SO.

41:21.246 --> 41:24.082
ARE YOU SURE
YOUR SISTER DIDN'T--
STOP WORRYING.

41:24.115 --> 41:25.917
I'VE BEEN SCARING HER
SINCE SHE WAS BORN.

41:25.951 --> 41:29.220
THERE'S NO WAY
SHE OR HER FRIENDS
ARE TURNING IN THAT VIDEO.

41:29.254 --> 41:31.189
TRUST ME.

41:34.760 --> 41:36.227
( floor creaking )

41:45.904 --> 41:47.706
( knock on door )

41:53.645 --> 41:57.315
OFFICER, HI.
UM, IS SOMETHING WRONG?

41:57.348 --> 42:00.318
NEIL.
WELL, WHAT, UH,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

42:00.351 --> 42:02.588
WE'RE HERE
ON OFFICIAL BUSINESS.

42:02.621 --> 42:05.857
OFFICER REYNOLDS, WILL YOU
PLEASE SURRENDER YOUR WEAPON?

42:06.925 --> 42:10.161
WHAT? WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

42:10.195 --> 42:12.764
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?
WHAT HAS HE DONE?

42:12.798 --> 42:14.800
GARRETT REYNOLDS,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

42:14.833 --> 42:17.636
FOR WHAT?
THE MURDER
OF ALISON DILAURENTIS.

42:20.271 --> 42:22.107
( cuffs locking shut )

42:46.998 --> 42:48.900
( buzzing )

42:50.001 --> 42:51.369
* MY HEART IS JUMPIN'

42:51.402 --> 42:53.371
* AND YOU STARTED SOMETHIN'

42:53.404 --> 42:55.907
* WITH THEM THERE EYES

42:55.941 --> 42:57.909
* OH, THEY'RE GONNA SPARKLE

42:57.943 --> 42:59.911
* THEY'RE GONNA BUBBLE

42:59.945 --> 43:03.281
* THEY'RE GONNA GET YA
IN A WHOLE MESS OF TROUBLE *

43:03.314 --> 43:04.750
* YOU'RE OVERWORKIN' 'EM

43:04.783 --> 43:06.017
* THERE'S DANGER LURKIN'

43:06.051 --> 43:08.687
* IN THEM THERE EYES

43:13.659 --> 43:15.761
I KNOW WHAT OUR DEAL WAS,

43:15.794 --> 43:19.731
BUT THIS IS A LOT MORE
THAN I BARGAINED FOR.
